168
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:56,139
Do you think I should forgive him?

169
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:59,200
After all, this is your personal matter.

170
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,299
As an outsider, it's not my place to judge.

171
00:11:01,299 --> 00:11:06,180
However, no matter what your decision is, I will support you.

172
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:20,859
Wei Yuan, I'm so lucky to have a sister like you.

173
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,900
Sheng Mian.

174
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:44,459
What can I do to make you forgive me?

175
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,879
Do you need something?

176
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,559
Sheng Mian,

177
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,000
I miss you.

178
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:09,139
You've drunk too much. Don't call me.

179
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:16,380
Sister, don't go home tonight. Stay here.

180
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:19,220
We haven't spent time together in so long.

181
00:12:19,220 --> 00:12:24,879
I really miss how we used to chat under the covers.

182
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:32,619
All right.

183
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:36,400
Then I won't leave tonight.

184
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:10,879
 I want to see you. 

185
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:13,479
 Can I come find you now? 

186
